name: Woody Woodpecker Racing
description: Prepare for the wildest ride of your life as Woody Woodpecker and 8 of his friends bring their brand of comic mischief to the raceways. Join the sly bird himself, Winnie Woodpecker, Chilly Willy and more as they throw dynamite, dodge rotten tomatoes, and drop tire tacks in a high-speed battle for the checkered flag.
